---
title: Apricot Haloumi, Chicken & Mumbai Veggie Toss with Garlic Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Here’s a hearty chicken and haloumi meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful haloumi
coated in apricot sauce meets roasted vegetables tossed with Mumbai-style spices, and there’s a tangy
yoghurt dressing to finish it off.
